@startuml
actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
boundary "System" as System

== Register Storage Area ==
Officer -> System : POST /api/storageareas\n(CreatingStorageAreaDto: name, type, bays, rows, tiers, distances)
System --> Officer : 201 Created\n(StorageAreaDto with Id, capacity, occupancy, docks, distances)

== Update Storage Area ==
Officer -> System : PUT/PATCH /api/storageareas/{id}\n(UpdateStorageAreaDto: description?, type?, capacity?, distances?)
System --> Officer : 200 OK\n(Updated StorageAreaDto)

== Query Storage Areas ==
Officer -> System : GET /api/storageareas/{id}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\n(StorageAreaDto)

Officer -> System : GET /api/storageareas?name={name}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\n(StorageAreaDto)

Officer -> System : GET /api/storageareas/distances?name={name}|id={id}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\n(List<StorageAreaDockDistanceDto>)

== Validation Rules ==
Officer -> System : Register/Update with occupancy > maxCapacity
System --> Officer : 400 Bad Request\n(BusinessRuleValidationException)

Officer -> System : Register with duplicated Name
System --> Officer : 409 Conflict\n(BusinessRuleValidationException)

Officer -> System : Reference non-existing Dock
System --> Officer : 400 Bad Request\n(BusinessRuleValidationException)
@enduml
